The {{nihongo|'''Katahara-machi Station'''|<U+7247><U+539F><U+753A><U+99C5>|Katahara-machi Eki}} is a [[city]] [[tram]] [[Metro station|station]] on the [[Many<U+014D>sen Takaoka Kid<U+014D> Line|Takaoka Kid<U+014D> Line]] located in [[Takaoka, Toyama|Takaoka]], [[Toyama Prefecture]], [[Japan]]. The station is sometimes called {{nihongo|'''Yamach<U+014D>suji Entrance'''|<U+5C71><U+753A><U+7B4B><U+5165><U+308A><U+53E3>|Yamach<U+014D>suji Iriguchi}}.

